            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>Scrape the <strong>inner</strong> <strong>seeds</strong> out of the cucumber using a teaspoon and set aside for later, then dice the rest</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
