    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> diced cucumber</strong>, <strong>chopped shallot</strong> and <strong>diced tomato </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>kachumber salad</strong></p>",
